name: Naomi's Nightmares of Nature
overview: From crocodiles to spiders, some of the planet's most feared beasties aren't as scary as you might think. Naomi Wilkinson travels the world to come face to face with Nightmares of Nature - animals that seem weird, dangerous or downright scary.
